      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine, factory-fresh condition with no signs of wear. Every component functions perfectly, and the car has been maintained to the highest possible standard, making it a rare find for a discerning collector or enthusiast.",
